%%{init: {'theme': 'dark', 'sequence': {'actorMargin': 60, 'width': 160, 'useMaxWidth': false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Caller
    participant I as Inference plugin
    participant H as aroundCompletion
    participant W as Workflow
    participant L as LLM

    C->>I: chatComplete
    I->>H: invokeHook — full prompt
    H->>W: execute
    W-->>W: ai.pii — anonymize + build tokenMap
    W->>H: call_site.proceed — anonymized prompt + tokenMap
    Note over H,W: Workflow suspended
    H->>I: proceedFn — anonymized prompt + tokenMap
    I->>L: connector call (stream)
    loop each chunk
        L-->>I: chunk
        I-->>C: de-anonymized chunk (inline restore)
    end
    I-->>H: assembled response
    Note over H,W: Workflow resumes
    H->>W: step output — response
    W-->>W: transform.pii_restore
    W-->>H: result
    H-->>I: hook result
    I-->>C: final result
